<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="description" content="SSL证书挂啦">
    <title>SSL证书挂啦</title>
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family:STKaitiSC-Black,STKaitiSC;
        }
        html, body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            min-width: 1040px;
            padding-bottom: 100px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .header {
            height: 100px;
            /*line-height: 100px;*/
            background-color: rgba(255, 249, 249, 1);
        }
        .header nav {
            width: 1040px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .menu {
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .menu a {
            line-height: 100px;
            color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 1);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .menu a:last-child {
            margin-left: 100px;
        }
        .menu a:hover {
            color: #F82045;
        }
        .header nav .nav-logo {
            display: flex;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .header nav .logo {
            width: 100px;
            height: 60px;
        }
        .header nav .logo-text {
            display: flex;
            margin-left: 10px;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }
        .logo-text-til {
            line-height: 1;
            font-size:36px;
            color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 1)
        }
        .logo-text-dec {
            font-size:14px;
            color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8)
        }
        main, .header nav, footer {
            width: 1040px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        main section {
            float: left;
            width: 50%;
            padding-top: 24px;
        }
        main section .phone {
            width: auto;
            max-width: 600px;
            height: 540px;
        }
        main section .title {
            font-size:48px;
            margin-top: 90px;
        }
        main section .dec {
            margin-bottom: 39px;
            font-size:18px;
            color: rgba(248, 32, 69, 1);
        }
        main section .item {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            padding: 13px 14px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(17, 17, 17, 1);
        }
        main section .item i {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
        main section .item-code {
            position: relative;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            padding: 5px 5px 5px 7px;
        }
        .layer {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 3;
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius:5px;
            border: 1px solid #111111;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .code {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
        }
        main section .item-code i {
            font-size: 35px;
            margin-right: 0;
        }
        main section .item:hover {
            background:linear-gradient(254deg,rgba(239,136,118,1) 0%,rgba(238,119,149,1) 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        main section .item-code:hover .layer{
            display: block;
        }
        footer {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            position: fixed;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            padding-top: 200px;
            padding-left: 23%;
            background: url("imgs/footer.png") no-repeat left bottom;
            background-size: 100% 250px;
        }
        footer div {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.3);
        }
        footer a {
            color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.3);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://at.alicdn.com/t/font_1855689_o0024yn5z5k.css">
</head>
<body>
<header class="header">
    <nav>
        <div>
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <img src="ssl-secure.png" class="logo" alt="">
               <div class="logo-text">
                   <span class="logo-text-til">SSL证书挂啦</span>
                   <span class="logo-text-dec">检测SSL证书状态，实时了解最新情况</span>
               </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="menu">
            <a href="/">首页</a>
            <a href="/policy" target="_blank">用户协议与隐私政策</a>
        </div>
    </nav>
</header>
<main>
    <section>
        <h2 class="title">SSL证书状态</h2>
        <p class="dec">不必每次都打开网页查看，一次查看所有网站的SSL证书</p>
        <div>            
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <img src="images/types-of-ssl-certificates.jpg" class="phone" alt="">
    </section>
</main>
<div style="clear: both"></div>
<footer>
    <div>山东风起云飞网络科技有限公司 | <a href="http://beian.miit.gov.cn/" target="_blank">鲁ICP备18057922号-2</a></div>
    <div>地址：山东省淄博市张店区华光路118号德泰堂国际商务大厦806室</div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
